<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-full">

    <div class="govuk-!-margin-top-4 govuk-!-padding-bottom-4 opss-border-bottom">

      <div class="govuk-grid-row">
        <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
          <h1 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">
            <% if @notification.product_name.present? %>
              <span class="govuk-caption-m">Product notification draft for: </span> <%= @notification.product_name %>
            <% else %>
              Add a cosmetic product
            <% end %>
          </h1>

          <p class="govuk-body opss-secondary-text">
          Complete the following tasks to add this cosmetic product.
          </p>

          <!--p class="govuk-body opss-secondary-text">
            <span class="govuk-!-display-block govuk-!-margin-bottom-4">Complete the following tasks to add a cosmetic product. Completing the first task may update the task list with additional tasks. </span>

            <span class="govuk-!-display-block">You can complete individual tasks again to change their details.</span>
            </p-->

            <details class="govuk-details opss-details--sm" data-module="govuk-details">
              <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
                <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
                  Help with adding a product
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="govuk-details__text">
                <p class="govuk-body-s">
                    Your progress in completing each task is saved as a working draft until you are ready to accept and submit it. Product drafts are stored in the <a href="#" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state">Cosmetic products page</a> from where you can resume and complete the remaining tasks at any time.</p>
                <p></p>
                <!--p class="govuk-body-s">
                    Completing the first task may change the list and the number of tasks.
                </p-->
                <p class="govuk-body-s">
                    Before you accept and submit a draft you can change information at any stage by completing individual tasks again. If you have added items (for multi-item kits) or nanomaterials, you can add or remove them individually at any stage.
                </p>
              </div>
            </details>

        </div>
        <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">
          <a href="<%= delete_responsible_person_delete_notification_path(@notification.responsible_person, @notification) %>" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state govuk-!-font-size-19 opss-text-align-right opss-text-underline-offset">
            Delete this draft
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>
